10 licensed short-term emergency and nonemergency hybrid medical
11 facility from providing other health care services including, but
12 not limited to, imaging, primary care, nonemergency care, and other
13 ancillary services.
14 D. Each separate facility location shall have a separate
15 license.
16 E. A license issued under this act is not transferable or
17 assignable.
18 F. Any person who is convicted of violating a provision of this
19 section shall be guilty of a misdemeanor. Each day of a continuing
20 violation constitutes a separate offense.
